			<h1>Tables</h1>
			<div class="breakout">
			Tables are a great way to present content on a page. A table consists of one or more rows; each row consists of one or more cells. Tables <b>are not</b> intended to be used for general layouts. The <a href="/styleguide-layout">12-column grid system</a> should be utilised in these cases.
			</div>
			
			<h2>Example</h2>

			<p>Table styling has been applied to the base element. No classes need be applied.</p>
			
			<div class="example-box">	
				<table>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td>						
							<table class="table-responsive">
								<thead>
								<tr>
									<th>#</th>
									<th>First Name</th>
									<th>Last Name</th>
									<th>ID Number</th>
								</tr>
								</thead>							
								<tbody>
								<tr>
									<th>1</th>
									<td>Mary</td>
									<td>Jones</td>
									<td>62843</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<th>2</th>
									<td>John</td>
									<td>Smith</td>
									<td>37225</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<th>3</th>
									<td>Frank</td>
									<td>Watson</td>
									<td>84775</td>
								</tr>
								</tbody>
							</table>		
						</td></tr>
						<tr><td class="example-code">
							<code>&lt;table class="table-responsive"&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;thead&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;tr&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;#&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;First Name&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;Last Name&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;ID Number&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;/tr&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;/thead&gt;</code><br>	
							<code>	&lt;tbody&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;tr&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;1&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;td&gt;Mary&lt;/td&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;td&gt;Jones&lt;/td&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;td&gt;62843&lt;/td&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;/tr&gt;</code><br>
							<code>	&lt;tr&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;th&gt;2&lt;/th&gt;</code><br>
							<code>		&lt;td&gt;John&lt;/td&gt;</code><br>
