				</table>
			</div>
			
			<hr>
			
			<h2>Responsive tables</h2>
			<p>Create responsive tables by adding <font color="red">.table-responsive</font> to any <font color="red">&lt;table&gt;</font> to make them scroll horizontally on small devices (under 768px). When viewing on anything larger than 768px wide, you will not see any difference in these tables.</p>
			
			
